procedureJavascriptCode.code:
/* Loop Code */
// Highest Volume Index, by quantum8
let length = 10

let candle = record.current
let volume = getElement('volumes', candle)
let totalVol = volume.buy + volume.sell


let highest = 0
let hvi = 0


variable.volArr.push(totalVol)
if (variable.volArr.length > length) {
    variable.volArr.splice(0, 1)

    highest = Math.max(...variable.volArr)

    variable.highestPrev = variable.highestPrev == 0 ? totalVol : variable.highestPrev
    variable.highestPrev = isFinite(variable.highestPrev) ? variable.highestPrev : totalVol

    hvi = totalVol * 100 / variable.highestPrev
}

variable.highestPrev = highest  // save for next iteration

variable.value = hvi

procedureJavascriptCode.name: New Procedure Javascript Code
procedureJavascriptCode.code:
/* Loop Code */
// Volume Strength Finder, by quantum8
const lookback = 10

let candle = record.current
let volume = getElement('volumes', candle)
let totalVol = volume.buy + volume.sell


let total_w = 0
let positive = 0
let negative = 0
let pdw = 0
let ndw = 0
let SSPV = 0
let SSNV = 0
let total_v = 0
let Pos = 0
let Neg = 0

variable.volArr.push(totalVol)
variable.closes.push(candle.close)
variable.highArr.push(candle.max)
variable.lowArr.push(candle.min)
if (variable.volArr.length > lookback) {
    variable.volArr.splice(0, 1)
    variable.closes.splice(0, 1)
    variable.highArr.splice(0, 1)
    variable.lowArr.splice(0, 1)

    for (i = variable.volArr.length - 2; i >= 0; i--) {
        total_w = variable.highArr[i] - variable.lowArr[i]
        positive = variable.closes[i] - variable.lowArr[i]
        negative = variable.highArr[i] - variable.closes[i]

        pdw = (positive / total_w) * 100
        ndw = (negative / total_w) * 100


        SSPV = (variable.volArr[i] * pdw) / 100 + SSPV
        SSNV = (variable.volArr[i] * ndw) / 100 + SSNV

    }

    total_v = SSPV + SSNV
    Pos = (SSPV / total_v) * 100
    Neg = (SSNV / total_v) * 100

}

/*console.log(" *** ")
console.log("close: ", candle.close)
console.log("SSPV: ", SSPV)
console.log("SSNV: ", SSNV)
console.log("Pos: ", Pos)
console.log("Neg: ", Neg)

console.log(" ")*/

variable.buyerVol = SSPV
variable.sellerVol = SSNV
variable.buyPerc = Pos
variable.sellPerc = Neg

procedureJavascriptCode.name: New Procedure Javascript Code
procedureJavascriptCode.code:
// Hawkeye Volume
const pLength1 = 200
const hvMa = 20
const div = 3.6


let candle = record.current
let volume = getElement('volumes', candle)
let AllVolume = volume.buy + volume.sell

let rangeVal = candle.max - candle.min
let rangeAvg = 0
let avVol = 0
let volumeA = 0


variable.rangeArr.push(rangeVal)
variable.volArr2.push(AllVolume)
if (variable.rangeArr.length > pLength1) {
    variable.rangeArr.splice(0, 1)
    variable.volArr2.splice(0, 1)

    rangeAvg = variable.rangeArr.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.rangeArr.length
    volumeA = variable.volArr2.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.volArr2.length
}

variable.volArr.push(AllVolume)
if (variable.volArr.length > hvMa) {
    variable.volArr.splice(0, 1)
    avVol = variable.volArr.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.volArr.length
}


// calculate colours
let high1 = variable.maxPrev
let low1 = variable.minPrev
let mid1 = variable.hl2Prev
high1 = high1 == 0 ? candle.max : high1
low1 = low1 == 0 ? candle.min : low1
mid1 = mid1 == 0 ? (candle.max + candle.min) / 2 : mid1

let u1 = mid1 + (high1 - low1) / div
let d1 = mid1 - (high1 - low1) / div

let r_enabled1 = (rangeVal > rangeAvg) && (candle.close < d1) && AllVolume > volumeA ? true : false
let r_enabled2 = candle.close < mid1 ? true : false
let r_enabled = r_enabled1 || r_enabled2 ? true : false

let condition = rangeVal < rangeAvg / 1.5 ? true : false
let g_enabled1 = candle.close > mid1 ? true : false
let g_enabled2 = (rangeVal > rangeAvg) && (candle.close > u1) && (AllVolume > volumeA) ? true : false
let g_enabled3 = (candle.max > high1) && (condition) && (AllVolume < volumeA) ? true : false
let g_enabled4 = (candle.min < low1) && (condition) && (AllVolume > volumeA) ? true : false
let g_enabled = g_enabled1 || g_enabled2 || g_enabled3 || g_enabled4 ? true : false

let volPrev = variable.volArr.at(-2)
volPrev = isFinite(volPrev) ? volPrev : 0
let gr_enabled1 = (rangeVal > rangeAvg) && (candle.close > d1) && (candle.close < u1) && (AllVolume > volumeA) && (AllVolume < volumeA * 1.5) && (AllVolume > volPrev) ? true : false
let gr_enabled2 = (rangeVal < rangeAvg / 1.5) && (AllVolume < volumeA / 1.5) ? true : false
let gr_enabled3 = (candle.close > d1) && (candle.close < u1) ? true : false
let gr_enabled = gr_enabled1 || gr_enabled2 || gr_enabled3 ? true : false

/*console.log(" *** ")
console.log("close: ", candle.close)
console.log(" ")*/

variable.volVal = AllVolume
variable.avVol = avVol

variable.col = gr_enabled ? 0 : g_enabled ? 1 : r_enabled ? 2 : 3

// save for next iteration
variable.maxPrev = candle.max
variable.minPrev = candle.min
variable.hl2Prev = (candle.max + candle.min) / 2
